data.description: Vacation at home year round! Lake living is wonderful. Boat, fish and enjoy the small sandy beach and the view. It doesn't get any better than this custom built 5 bedroom 3 bath home with plenty of room and extras. This home has been upgraded throughout to have SMART HOME capabilities. The entire home has been remodeled, the kitchen is new in 2021 as is the flooring throughout, fresh paint, high end commercial model water heater, motion lights in several areas. Nearly all of the areas are remotely controlled. The added features are a laundry chute from the 2nd floor to the lower floor, the utility is set up for 2 stackable washers and dryers, WIFI is wired for the entire house, there are cameras in the garage, at the driveway, back yard, and front door which covers the rest of the street areas. The garage door openers have battery back ups so you are never locked out during electrical outages! The owners are leaving a 110" pull down screen and projector in the media room as well as an upstairs wall mounted tv. Furnace/AC 5 years old. Lake dues $100.00 a year.
